<AbstractNarration>This award provides funding to Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University (VPI), Arun G. Phadke, Principal Investigator, for the support of a three-year, Combined Research-Curriculum Development (CRCD) project entitled, "Expansion of a Module Based Multimedia Courseware for Curriculum Enhancement in Power System Education."  The objective of this collaborative project between VPI and Iowa State University (ISU) is to enhance the existing web-based, modular, multimedia courseware created for the PowerLearn project and improve its effectiveness as a curriculum development tool.</AbstractNarration>
